Looking in the 2.1 code, doc, language packs, fragment.xml content has never
been translatable using a fragment.properties.
The keys appearing in the fragment.xml were translated in the plugin.properties
of the plugin to which the fragment was attached to.

The code in charge of doing the translation in 2.1 was doing the following call:
class PluginDescriptor {
...

private static final String DEFAULT_BUNDLE_NAME = "plugin";

public ResourceBundle getResourceBundle(Locale targetLocale) {
  ...
  ResourceBundle.getBundle(DEFAULT_BUNDLE_NAME, targetLocale, resourceLoader);
  ...
} 
}

The fix provided by Jeff is sufficient.
